$ SAS data step: modify

The `modify` statement can be used to change values in a → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/data-sets[data set]. 

The following example shows that the dataset set is not recreated with a modify statement:

gh|about-SAS|/programming/data-step/modify/creation-modification-date.sas||


sa:
  → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/data-sets/in-place-editing[In place editing]
